verse Regions</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From arid deserts to freezing tundra, navigate challenging environments and manage their effects on your Nexomon.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1196630/extras/9f900e2e8549ca6db54b4beaa2dafae1.poster.avif?t=1728893747\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1196630/extras/9f900e2e8549ca6db54b4beaa2dafae1.webm?t=1728893747\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1196630/extras/9f900e2e8549ca6db54b4beaa2dafae1.mp4?t=1728893747\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Immerse yourself in the world of Nexomon</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uncover secrets, stumble upon side-quests and encounter a raft of eccentric characters.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Train hard to become the greatest</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dynamic difficulty will see the world around you get more challenging as you progress, as even defeated trainers come back stronger than before and ready to battle again!</p>",
